flowchart LR
  %% Predict Track tool flowchart
  A[Incoming tool call: `predict_track`\nargs: selected_features, features, open_ui, numeric keys] --> B{Has numeric keys or `open_ui`?}
  B -- Yes --> C[Return action: open UI]
  B -- No --> D{Has explicit `selected_features`?}
  D -- No --> E[No features provided -> Ask user to select interests]
  D -- Yes --> F[Build feature row from selected features]
  F --> G[Load model artifacts from `ml_model/`]
  G --> H{Model bundle available?}
  H -- Yes --> I[Run model inference -> predicted label, confidence, top_predictions]
  H -- No --> J[Fallback rule-based predictor -> simple label and confidence 0.25/0.5]
  I --> K[Return prediction artifact: label, confidence, category, source, top_predictions]
  J --> K
  E --> C
  style K fill:#bff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
  classDef note fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#f0c36d;